roduction of high-$p_{T}$ hadrons in\ncomparison with the usual phenomenological Tsallis distribution function at the\nsame values of $q$. The $q$-duality of the Tsallis normalized and unnormalized\nstatistics for the massive particles was studied.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Mar 2019 16:53:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Feb 2020 10:57:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-09"}
