 periods, and for\n$\\ell'/\\ell \\to 0$ and $\\Delta U'/k_B T \\gg 1$ agrees closely with mean\nfirst-passage time estimates currently employed, which depend solely on the\nfine-scale energy barrier.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Mar 2019 23:12:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-22"}
