at\nmatch major cosmic ray abundances (Z/H)GCRS to within 35 % with no free\nparameters. Independently confirming grain injection, (Z/H)GCRS shows no\ndetectable contribution of Fe from SN Ia, although producing ~1/2 Fe in ISM,\nbut there is also no dust in SN Ia remnants, unlike CCSN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Mar 2019 02:29:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2019 20:04:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
